PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO, namely the Hon. JOHN W. MORDEN, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from November 17 to November 21, 1995, in the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
